# BUET Library Proxy Authentication File
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Add one line per user. Format: username:encrypted_password
#
# Generate entries using:
#   python proxy/generate_htpasswd.py <username> <password>
#
# Example:
#   python proxy/generate_htpasswd.py buetadmin mysecurepassword
#   # Copy the output line below
#
# Or on Linux/macOS with Apache:
#   htpasswd -nbB buetadmin mysecurepassword >> proxy/.htpasswd
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# IMPORTANT: Remove this comment and add real user entries before production!
# The proxy will NOT work without at least one valid user entry.

